    (defn gain [f g x]
      (- (log-pdf f x) (log-pdf g x)))
    (defn integrand [f g x]
      (* (gain f g x) (pdf f x)))
    (plot/plot (partial gain p1 p2) [-100 100])
    (plot/plot (partial integrand p1 p2) [-100 100])
    ​
    #'distributions.core/gain
    #'distributions.core/integrand

    (defn mc-reducer [current-estimate nx]
      (let [[n x] nx]
        (/ (+ (* n current-estimate) (gain p1 p2 x)) (inc n))))
    (def qi-list (map (fn [x] (kullback-leibler-qi p1 p2 x)) (range 2 2000)))
    (def mc-list-1 (reductions mc-reducer 0 (map vector (iterate inc 0) (sample p1 2000))))
    (def mc-list-2 (reductions mc-reducer 0 (map vector (iterate inc 0) (sample p1 2000))))
    (def mc-list-3 (reductions mc-reducer 0 (map vector (iterate inc 0) (sample p1 2000))))
    ​

    #'distributions.core/qi-list
    #'distributions.core/mc-list-1
    #'distributions.core/mc-list-2
    #'distributions.core/mc-list-3
    x
     
    (plot/compose
